I"<p>Sulyvahn, previously High Inquisitor of the Church of Malorn, claimed to be over a thousand years old when he captured Hubert and Ulrach. While he revealed little of substance, he was adamant that his choice to overthrow the Queen of Lundis was for the good of its people - that he would drag the race of men kicking and screaming into the next age whether they liked it or not.</p>

<p>The party killed Sulyvahn during the storming of White Tower. His final words were: “Nathaniel - do not let them tell you who you are.”</p>
